Bundled SuiteSparse Components — License Information
=====================================================

CppODE bundles minimal subsets of the following SuiteSparse libraries
by Timothy A. Davis et al. for sparse LU factorization via KLU.
No modifications have been made to the source code; only a symbol-prefix
header (cppode_ss_prefix.h) is used to avoid linker collisions.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
KLU — sparse LU factorization (Gilbert-Peierls algorithm with BTF)
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copyright (c) 2004-2022, University of Florida. All Rights Reserved.
Authors: Timothy A. Davis and Ekanathan Palamadai.
SPDX-License-Identifier: LGPL-2.1+

------------------------------------------------------------------------
BTF — permutation to block triangular form
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copyright (c) 2004-2022, University of Florida. All Rights Reserved.
Author: Timothy A. Davis.
SPDX-License-Identifier: LGPL-2.1+

------------------------------------------------------------------------
AMD — approximate minimum degree ordering
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copyright (c) 1996-2022, Timothy A. Davis, Patrick R. Amestoy,
and Iain S. Duff. All Rights Reserved.
SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-3-Clause

------------------------------------------------------------------------
COLAMD — column approximate minimum degree ordering
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copyright (c) 1998-2022, Timothy A. Davis. All Rights Reserved.
Authors: Stefan I. Larimore and Timothy A. Davis.
SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-3-Clause

------------------------------------------------------------------------
SuiteSparse_config — common configuration for all SuiteSparse modules
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copyright (c) 2012-2023, Timothy A. Davis. All Rights Reserved.
SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-3-Clause

------------------------------------------------------------------------
All components are available from https://github.com/DrTimothyAldenDavis/SuiteSparse
